Six steps before run your test forum:

1. Create virtual environment:

    virtualenv --clear --no-site-packages /your/path/to/environment

2. Activate virtual environment:

    source /your/path/to/environment/bin/activate
    
3. Install project requirements:

    pip install -r build/pip_requirements.txt
    
4. Sync project applications with test database:

    ./manage.py syncdb --all
    
5. Run development server:

    ./manage.py runserver

6. Open browser tab with address 127.0.0.1:8000
